Package: BsplineQuantRegGui
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Shiny Interface for BsplineQuantReg
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-07-22
Authors@R: person("Alexandre", "Abbes", email = "alexandre.abbes@proton.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A user-friendly interactive Shiny interface for the BsplineQuantReg package, 
    enabling quantile regression using B-splines with shape constraints. 
    Features include interactive knot placement, per-region constraint specification, 
    CSV/Excel data import, demo presets, and reproducible R code generation.
    Based on the method described in Alexandre Abbes (2025).
